---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Buttons from "../componets/Buttons.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Volunteer"
  hero_img="img_karrusel/frivillig_figma.png"
  hero_tekst="Volunteer"
>
  <div class="main_luft">
    <h2 class="principles_luft">Our principles</h2>
    <section>
      <p>
        Volunteering at a festival is a vibrant tapestry woven with threads of
        camaraderie, dedication, and the sheer joy of contributing to a shared
        experience. Festivals, whether celebrating music, culture, or art,
        thrive on the energy and passion of volunteers who dedicate their time
        and efforts to ensure the event's success.
      </p>
      <p>
        Principles such as collaboration and teamwork form the foundation of
        successful festival volunteering. Volunteers often find themselves
        working in diverse teams, each member bringing their unique skills and
        perspectives to the table. This collaborative approach not only enhances
        the efficiency of the festival operations but also enriches the overall
        experience for both volunteers and attendees.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="article_grid">
      <article class="bar_grid">
        <h2>Volunteer bar and food truck crew</h2>
        <p>
          Join the festival fun by becoming a volunteer at the bars and food
          trucks! It's a fantastic way to be part of the excitement and
          contribute to the vibrant atmosphere. As a volunteer, you'll help
          serve drinks or delicious bites, ensuring everyone has a great time.
          No experience is needed – just bring your positive energy and
          willingness to help. It's a chance to make new friends, soak in the
          festival vibes, and be a key player in creating an unforgettable
          experience for all!
        </p>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Volunteer clean up crew</h2>
        <p>
          Join the clean-up crew and be a festival hero! As a volunteer, you'll
          help keep the festival grounds tidy by picking up litter. It's a
          chance to make a meaningful impact and be part of a fantastic team.
          Ready to create a spotless and unforgettable festival experience? Sign
          up now!
        </p>
      </article>

      <article>
        <h2>Volunteer security crew</h2>
        <p>
          Join the volunteer security team and play a crucial role in ensuring a
          safe and enjoyable experience for all. As a security volunteer, you'll
          contribute to maintaining a secure environment, assisting
          festival-goers, and adding to the positive vibes.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="stage_grid">
        <h2>Volunteer stage building crew - Pre festival</h2>
        <p>
          Join the volunteer stage-building team and be a part of creating the
          magic before the event kicks off. No previous construction experience
          required – just bring your passion and eagerness to contribute. As a
          volunteer, you'll be instrumental in assembling stages, organizing
          equipment, and ensuring everything is set up for an unforgettable
          festival experience. Ready to be a vital part of the stage-building
          crew? Sign up now and let's craft an extraordinary festival together!
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="form">
      <h2 class="forms_h2">Hold yourself updated with a newsletter!</h2>

